author: Perez Hilton
title: A Snake Got Caught In This Woman's Ear Gauge!
text:
As Samuel L. Jackson would (probably) say:
I HAVE HAD IT WITH THESE MOTHERFUCKING SNAKES IN THIS MOTHERFUCKING PLANE EARLOBE! 
Last week, Ashley Glawe was innocently playing with her pet snake Bart when the reptile decided to slither away... into her gauged earlobe!
Related: Singer Performs 45 Minutes After Being Bitten By Snake 
The situation was so bad, the Portland-native had to go to the emergency room!
She posted on Facebook : 
Luckily, medical experts numbed her ear, stretched it out even more, and was able to get Bart out.
At the end of the day, Miz Glawe still loves her pet snake even though he caused quite the commotion!
[ Image via Ashley Glawe/ Facebook . ]
